{"tid":1473862,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"大媽團譴責商台去錯港台","createTime":"2019-08-15T03:29:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T04:19:52.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"56fcf39077bce58507dde1edb975e084a79b8863","tid":1473862,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T03:29:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20190815/20749131\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190815%2F20749131&d=uCt0JTl3CznPmZ5dgdQeg3%2B3Qbouwy6U%2BTFwRHAqvaY%3D&h=7e128e65\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190815%2F20749131&h=0ec00201\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20190815/20749131</a><br />\n<br />\n大媽團譴責商台去錯港台<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190815/large/1565791216_9fa7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190815%2Flarge%2F1565791216_9fa7.jpg&h=e412633f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大媽團昨早到港台門口，卻舉着譴責商台的橫額。互聯網圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n港台和商台903都有DJ響應8.5三罷，周日克警濫捕，翌日903全日停播節目，讓聽眾向政府和警察提問。昨日約20名大媽大叔，站在廣播道香港電台電視大廈門外抗議商台，拉橫額「強烈譴責商業電台立場偏頗」，叫了十多分鐘口號就收工。至下午，大媽團去到商台，但卻舉着「立場與民為敵，煞停香港電台」的標語，似乎再次去錯地方。對於有大媽拉橫額，商台對外事務部表示：「商業電台一直維護新聞自由，持平客觀為民發聲，歡迎各界繼續反映意見。」<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：阿Sa舞台劇改期避遊行<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190815/large/1565791215_dc90.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190815%2Flarge%2F1565791215_dc90.jpg&h=cf94bee1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大媽團昨午再到商台門口，卻是譴責港台。互聯網圖片<br />\n<br />\n此外，十幾個大叔大媽大前日曾到《蘋果日報》大樓外示威，他們舉橫額影相後，約20分鐘即等巴士走人，大媽團表示是自發來抗議，不是由組織策劃。大媽前日也有到now TV「開工」，不過就網民嘲笑：「新聞部唔喺呢度！」<br />\n<br />\n採訪：黃曉妍  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n央視發功邀藝人表態群星效忠保飯碗 千嬅被指港獨「堅決反對和強烈憤慨」<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n阿Sa舞台劇改期避遊行<br />\n<br />\n阿Sa舞台劇改期避遊行<br />\n關淑怡生日斥警殺害市民<br />\n央視發功邀藝人表態 群星效忠保飯碗千嬅被指港獨「堅決反對和強烈憤慨」"},{"pid":"9825baea5873a28a7d2e069505fc2476cd3879c1","tid":1473862,"uid":299276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T03:35:41.000Z","msg":"JM9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e86be48f5a287d44efb5a3fab15f1901bd4d7b82","tid":1473862,"uid":94402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T03:47:31.000Z","msg":"唉...霞姨表示想收番個飯盒"},{"pid":"3f8b073404e1069678360a9c6166dbc60e3c0982","tid":1473862,"uid":156363,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T03:51:32.000Z","msg":"拿拿聲打卡影相交去人民日報交差，睇唔切塊牌。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a00924e23652cf5575c1b835aba7b7d6b5779c60","tid":1473862,"uid":171992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T03:52:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/6yR8ycR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6yR8ycR.jpg&h=a587efad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141044_b70c4022f89dcf5617302fe3f20434af.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141044_b70c4022f89dcf5617302fe3f20434af.jpeg&h=b7bac505&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141056_6689ba9867dc55e5e3b796d75180758d.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F